testsuite.name: com.example.test.flow.IOUFlowTests

testcase.name: SignedTransaction returned by the flow is signed by the initiator
SignedTransaction returned by the flow is signed by the acceptor
recorded transaction has no inputs and a single output, the input IOU
flow records a transaction in both parties' transaction storages
flow records the correct IOU in both parties' vaults
